            <lg xml:id="TK559">
<l>muṟaikōṭi maṉṉavaṉ ceyyi ṉuṟaikōṭi </l>
<l>yollātu vāṉam peyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the king acts contrary to justice, rain will become unseasonable, and the heavens will withhold their showers.</l>
